{"tid":1895181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"KF94在韓被炒貴6倍，在韓港人反託友人香港寄口罩","createTime":"2020-02-24T11:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:49:50.000Z","uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d84e120b3367dfb5109f6020c0d7230bef5116b7","tid":1895181,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"南韓爆發武漢肺炎，在韓港人警惕疫情。在首爾修讀韓語課程的吳小姐向《蘋果》稱，市內旅遊區已較以往冷清，「明顯冇咁多中國人」，但其他地區仍算熱鬧。她指，之前韓國人戴口罩比例約為一半半，現時街上已有約9成人會戴口罩，但室內則無人戴口罩，<span style=\"color: red;\">「識幾個韓國朋友都表示唔擔心，話對韓國醫療有信心」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n物資方面，吳小姐說，消毒酒精等供應充足，<span style=\"color: red;\">口罩雖有貨但被炒貴，以她所知，有KF94口罩已炒至3,500韓元一個（約22元港幣）</span>，同款口罩以前每個售價僅約500韓元（約3元港幣）。她指，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使在網上購物平台以正價購買，賣家亦不會出貨</span>。她又說，自己僅餘約20個口罩存貨，已託朋友由香港寄口罩予她，「之前朋友叫我喺呢邊搵（口罩）寄返香港，而家變成佢寄返畀我」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/qtj0AVZhPpjSeAB0qjrGLMKJ31Y=/802x601/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/MVR7ZMN7P5OAVNU5JRZQE7MO5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fqtj0AVZhPpjSeAB0qjrGLMKJ31Y%3D%2F802x601%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FMVR7ZMN7P5OAVNU5JRZQE7MO5I.jpg&h=fc5ea2f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f37a12d3c90f248d74acdc3228e3bb1fc764761","tid":1895181,"uid":58918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"我都對南韓有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e25d14cb84d546278f285cd60ba5c9f4b8031ac","tid":1895181,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"同香港差唔多價位"},{"pid":"c24b050afc16e127f082711780578c71e84396ee","tid":1895181,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"李屍朝鮮2:大邱篇"},{"pid":"2a966516320e628ae9a1f57a558bcca9fb9131e3","tid":1895181,"uid":194298,"l